<% provide(:title, 'Belief') %>
<div class="row text-center">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <section class="main-photo bg-img fast-height-trans" id="home-main">
    </section>
 </div>
</div>

<div class="row block-spacing-sml" id="faith-statement">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <div class="row medium-centered">
      <div class="medium-11 small-12 columns small-only-text-center">
        <h3><strong>Our Foundational Beliefs</strong></h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="small-12 columns">
 <div class="row text-center">
  <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns responsive-white-border-left" id="beliefs-1">
   <div class="row cf">
    <div class="top responsive-square">
     <h5><strong>One God existing in three persons: Father, Son and Holy Spirit</strong></h5>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom responsive-square">
     <h5><strong>We believe that there is one God (Deut. 6:4), eternally existing in three persons - Father, Son, and Holy Spirit (2 Cor. 13:14) - who created the heavens and the earth (Gen. 1:1).</strong></h5>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
  <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns responsive-white-border" id="beliefs-2">
   <div class="row cf">
    <div class="top responsive-square">
     <h5><strong>Life, death and resurrection of Jesus Christ, who is the Lamb of God</strong></h5>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom responsive-square">
     <h5><strong>We believe that Jesus Christ is the Lamb of God who died for sins once for all (1 Peter 3:18-19) and rose from death in three days, according to the Scriptures (1 Cor. 15:3-4)</strong></h5>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
  <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns responsive-white-border-right" id="beliefs-3">
   <div class="row cf">
    <div class="top responsive-square">
     <h5><strong>Jesus saved us from sin and eternal death.</strong></h5>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom responsive-square">
     <h5><strong>We believe that Jesus Christ (as fully God and fully man) is our Lord and God, our Savior and Redeemer who saved us from sin and eternal death (Eph. 1:7).</strong></h5>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </div>
 <div class="row text-center">
  <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns responsive-white-border-left" id="beliefs-4">
   <div class="row cf">
    <div class="top responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content"><strong>Salvation is by God's mercy and grace and is a completely free gift.</strong></h5>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content"><strong>We believe that it is by God's mercy and grace that we have been saved through faith (Titus 3:5), and this salvation is a completely free gift from God (Eph. 2:8-9).</strong></h5>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
  <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns responsive-white-border" id="black">
   <div class="row cf">
    <div class="top responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content" style="color: white;"><strong>The Holy Spirit dwells in us, intercedes for us and sanctifies us.</strong></h5>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content" style="color: white;"><strong>We believe in the Holy Spirit who indwells in those who believe (1 Cor. 3:16), and that He intercedes for us (Rom. 8:26-27) and sanctifies us (2 Thes. 2:13) to be conformed to the image of Christ (Rom. 8:29).</strong></h5>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
  <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns responsive-white-border-right" id="black">
   <div class="row cf">
    <div class="top responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content" style="color: white;"><strong>The Bible is the eternal Word of God.</strong></h5>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content" style="color: white;"><strong>We believe in the Holy Scripture (the Bible) as the only authoritative, inspired, trustworthy, and eternal Word of God (2 Tim. 3:16; 2 Pet. 1:21).</strong></h5>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </div>
 <div class="row text-center">
  <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns responsive-white-border-left" id="black">
   <div class="row cf">
    <div class="top responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content" style="color: white;"><strong>Christ will come again.</strong></h5>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content" style="color: white;"><strong>We believe in Christ's Second Coming, and that on that day, those who were dead in Christ will rise first. Then those who are alive will be lifted together in the cloud to be with God forever (1 Thes. 4:16-17).</strong></h5>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
  <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns responsive-white-border" id="black">
   <div class="row cf">
    <div class="top responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content" style="color: white;"><strong>As God's elect, we have an eternal life that can never be lost.</strong></h5>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom responsive-square">
     <h5 class="cf-content" style="color: white;"><strong>We believe in the eternal life and relationship with God, and, as God's elect, that this life is eternally secure and will never be lost (Jn. 10:27-29; 1 Pet. 1:3-5).</strong></h5>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
   <div class="medium-4 small-12 columns responsive-white-border-right" id="beliefs-9">
    <div class="row cf bg-img" id="faith-statement-cross">
   </div>
  </div>  

 </div> 

<div class="row separation-2">

</div>
</div>
